6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to firearms; amending 21 O.S. 2021,
Section 1277, which relates to the unlawful carry of
8 firearms; authorizing the carry of firearms on
certain designated property; allowing an individual
9 to openly carry a handgun on specific property with
permission; and providing an effective date.
